node.text: Hey guys!  It’s been SO hard not teaching my fitness classes.  Luckily I keep getting Lots of requests for another workout, cause I need this as much as you do! 🙌🏼 This might be my favorite set of numbers!  Hope you’ll dance with me and share this with a friend 😘

node.title: Get yo fit on with Liz!

I’m in love!  Meet my new best friend the Shark® Wandvac™ System from @sharkcleaning #ad! Friends…Life just got a whole lot easier!

Not only does this sage Shark® Wandvac™ System look pretty enough to leave out for display, it’s so lightweight and easy to carry around your home!  Slide to watch how I turn this cordless vacuum into a hand vacuum in seconds🤚🏼! Suddenly vacuuming feels like FUN instead of a chore! ✨NEW RUG ✨(Swipe to see the other side of the room!)

.
Need help finding a special rug too?  I’ll share a few of my favorites from @luluandgeorgia in stories!  @shop.ltk 
.

Kids are back to school! 🙌🏼 while kids are away… parents will play! 
.
I’ve never been more excited to share something with you!  Meet our new fat tire @radpowerbikes 🙌🏼 This Rad Rover 5 is perfect for our desert terrain, and perfect for a day date with your sweetheart! ❤️ check out my stories for details 🙌🏼 #gifted 
.

node.text:
🍂 What colors are you excited to introduce this fall season?!? … give me all the rust tones! 🙌🏼
.
This space turned into a teenage man cave over the summer.  Now that my kids are back in school it’s time to reclaim the house, and make it pretty again!  Added a few pops of warm fall colors and suddenly this space feels new again!  Everything linked @shop.ltk 
.

node.text:
Let’s talk photo editing...
.
I took this picture, and assumed I could never lighten it enough to actually share it on my feed. (Swipe for before). Isn’t editing just like magic?  It’s amazing what free editing apps can do for your photography!  Great photos are so important when creating a beautifully curated feed.  Imagine growing your instagram account just by editing! (See full editing tutorial in my stories) 
.
Free apps used:
-Snapseed 
-Tezza
.

node.text:
If you have kids, do you ever take them on day dates?  Had the best day with my daughter.  Just her and I having some bonding time shopping, and having lunch today!  Made me realize just how quickly time goes.  Enjoy them while they are little, and still want to spend time with you. 🥺
.
When I got home I shared some tips on making your bedding feel more full, and luxurious!  See stories for more… !!!
.

Hi friends…where are you escaping to this summer?  We are at our cabin for a few days, so I shared a little tour of our favorite spaces including my kids bunk room! It’s honestly the log walls for me. 🙌🏼
.
I have to say I was stressing about climbing up to make these beds, but we added @beddys bedding to each bunk and it’s a total game changer!! Use code: FREEDOM24 for 24% off! 
.

node.text:
👉🏽Swipe for my favorite TRANSFORMATION!!! What do you think?
.
Proof that you can transform something in your home you don’t like, into something you LOVE! 
These cabinets at the top of our stairs have been a big brown eye sore for years!  We had contemplated replacing these cabinets, but I’m so glad we decided on a DIY facelift instead. I hope this motivates you to reinvent what you already have, and make it something you love!! 🙌🏼
.

node.text:
What was your favorite thing you did today?!? ☀️ It was a perfect Sunday!  Spent the morning at church, then came home to CHILL with my family!  Best kind of days are days spent with the ones you love the most, doing absolutely NOTHING. ❤️ Am I right? 
.
I shared my @arhaus artwork was finally on sale and you sold them out completely!  I did notice that my Ashby sofa was on major sale, so I linked that and a new cabinet arriving soon that I think you will LOVE!!!! (See stories) 
.
